'''格洛斯特郡旗'''（Gloucestershire flag），是[[英國|英國]][[英格蘭|英格蘭]][[格洛斯特郡|格洛斯特郡]]的旗幟<ref>[https://web.archive.org/web/20120619002705/http://www.soglos.com/children/27652/Design-a-Gloucestershire-flag ''Design a Gloucestershire flag''] SoGlos.com, 29 January 2008. Retrieved 13 February 2014 from Internet Archive.</ref>。格洛斯特郡旗為綠底，上有藍色和白色的十字圖案，設計者是傑瑞米·賓陶（Jeremy Bentall）<ref>[http://www.bbc.co.uk/gloucestershire/content/image_galleries/gloucs_flag_gallery.shtml?1 Photos: Gloucestershire's new flag] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/gloucestershire/content/image_galleries/gloucs_flag_gallery.shtml?1 |date=20150925054317 }} [[BBC_Gloucestershire|BBC Gloucestershire]], July 2008. Retrieved 13 February 2014.</ref>。郡旗在2008年3月開始徵求設計方案，是該郡設立1,000週年紀念活動的一部分。

